author: Reuters
title: Janus fund, overseen by Bill Gross, had $4.5 mln inflow in Aug -Morningstar
text:
NEW YORK, Sept 10 The Janus Global Unconstrained Bond Fund, overseen by widely followed investor Bill Gross, had $4.5 million of inflows in August, according to Morningstar data.
Total assets in the fund at the end of August were $1.42 billion, Morningstar said.
(Reporting By Jennifer Ablan)
